\\\\
&=\dfrac{u'(x)v(x)-u(x)v'(x)}{[v(x)]^2}
\end{align}$

Let's differentiate!

$\begin{align}
&\phantom{=}\dfrac{dy}{dx}
\\\\
&=\dfrac{d}{dx}\left(\dfrac{\ln(x)}{\sin(x)}\right)
\\\\
&=\dfrac{\dfrac{d}{dx}(\ln(x))\sin(x)-\ln(x)\dfrac{d}{dx}(\sin(x))}{(\sin(x))^2}&&\gray{\text{The quotient rule}}
\\\\
